<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Promo iCHEF 29€</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;700;900&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
        }

        /* FORMAT POST INSTAGRAM (1080x1080 rendu proportionnel) */
        .promo-card {
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0A0A 0%, #000000 100%);
            border: 2px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), inset 0 0 40px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 40px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* EFFET LUMIÈRE EN ARRIÈRE-PLAN */
        .promo-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
            z-index: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100%;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: #D4AF37;
        }

        .badge {
            background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #D4AF37;
            color: #D4AF37;
            padding: 6px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .main-message {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .main-message h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .main-message p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #A0A0A0;
            margin: 0;
            max-width: 80%;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .price-block {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .price {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #D4AF37;
            line-height: 0.8;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .period {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .feature-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #E0E0E0;
        }

        .feature-item::before {
            content: '✔';
            color: #10B981;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .cta {
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            color: #000000;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .guarantee {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #777777;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="promo-card">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="logo">iCHEF<span>.</span></div>
                <div class="badge">Pack Essentiel</div>
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                <h1>Digitalisez<br>votre salle.</h1>
                <p>La puissance d'un système de commande et de paiement de dernière génération. Sans commission.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="price-block">
                <div class="price">29€</div>
                <div class="period">/ mois<br><span style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 300; color: #777;">Sans engagement</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature-item">Menu QR interactif illimité</div>
                <div class="feature-item">Paiement Stripe (0% de commission iCHEF)</div>
                <div class="feature-item">Caisse rapide & Synchronisation Cloud</div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <div class="guarantee">Installation en 5 min</div>
                <div class="cta">Déployer maintenant</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
